comments: Curry (DAL) moves into Bonga's (WAS) path and initiates the marginal lower body contact.  Bonga does not go through Curry's space and cause him to go to the floor.
Hachimura (WAS) slightly extends his arms and makes marginal contact to Porzingis (DAL) as he tries to slip the pick. The contact causes him to make incidental contact with Bertans (WAS).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) briefly places both hands on Bertans' (WAS) hips, but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Beal (WAS).  After the release of the shot, Finney-Smith makes marginal contact to Beal.
Beal (WAS) makes some contact to Kleber's (DAL) arm on the rebound, but the contact does not affect his ability to maintain control of the ball or dislodge him.
Beal (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Curry (DAL) as Curry extends both arms and pushes off of Beal to gain space.
Finney-Smith (DAL) immediately slides his hand off of Hachimura (WAS) as he engages on the screen and the contact is marginal.

Smith (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Brunson (DAL) as he jumps away from Brunson and avoids contact. Brunson slightly extends his leg as part of his shooting motion, but the contact to Smith is marginal.
During the rebound, Hachimura (WAS) and Kleber (DAL) engage and separate.
Bertans (WAS) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith (DAL) as he disengages and cuts to the basket.
Kleber (DAL) jumps into and makes contact to Bertans' (WAS) body during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Bonga (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact initiated by Porzingis (DAL) during the driving shot attempt.  Bonga cleanly blocks Porzingis' shot attempt at the basket.
Porzingis (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Beal (WAS).
Wagner (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
During the drive, Bonga (WAS) is late to establish himself in a legal guarding position as he makes contact to Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) body and the contact affects his SQBR.
Wright (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the play at the basket by Beal (WAS).
During the inbound, Mahinmi (WAS) and Kleber (DAL) mutually engage and separate underneath the basket.  Bertans (WAS) cleanly deflects the inbound pass.
During the inbound, Wagner (WAS) and Marjanovic (DAL) mutually engage and disengage under the basket.
